OL,3,CState schools falling behind private
OL,4,Cschools in AI 'digital divide' ` report
OL,6,FState schools are falling behind
OL,7,Fprivate schools in adopting artificial
OL,8,Fintelligence, a survey has suggested.
OL,10,FIndependent schools, or those in
OL,11,Fwealthier areas, are likely to have
OL,12,Fgreater access to resources and can
OL,13,Fafford to invest in more sophisticated
OL,14,FAI solutions, according to a Sutton
OL,15,FTrust report.
OL,17,FThe social mobility charity is calling
OL,18,Fon the Government to tackle the
OL,19,F"digital divide" among pupils to
OL,20,Fimprove their access to the benefits
OL,21,Fof AI.
