OL,3,CState schools falling behind private
OL,4,Cschools in AI 'digital divide' ` report
OL,6,FThe poll, of more than 10,000 teachers
OL,7,Facross England, suggests private
OL,8,Fschool teachers are more than twice as
OL,9,Flikely to have received formal AI
OL,10,Ftraining than their state school peers
OL,11,F(45% vs 21%).
OL,13,FPrivate schools are "ahead of the
OL,14,Fgame" on setting AI policies,
OL,15,Fdedicating staff to oversee its use,
OL,16,Fand providing staff training and
OL,17,Fresources compared to state schools,
OL,18,Fthe report found.
