OL,3,CState schools falling behind private
OL,4,Cschools in AI 'digital divide' ` report
OL,6,FThe Teacher Tapp poll, carried out
OL,7,Fbetween April 3 and 14, suggested that
OL,8,F17% of state school teachers said they
OL,9,Fdo not use AI at all compared to only
OL,10,F8% of private school teachers.
OL,12,FPrivate schools are three times more
OL,13,Flikely to have a clear school-wide
OL,14,Fstaff strategy on using AI than state
OL,15,Fschools (27% vs 9%), according to the
OL,16,Freport.
