OL,3,CState schools falling behind private
OL,4,Cschools in AI 'digital divide' ` report
OL,6,FNearly a quarter (24%) of state school
OL,7,Fteachers said they were not at all
OL,8,Fconfident using AI tools in their
OL,9,Frole, compared to just 15% of private
OL,10,Fschool teachers, the poll suggested.
OL,12,FPrivate school teachers were more
OL,13,Flikely than their state school peers
OL,14,Fto use AI for a number of tasks `
OL,15,Fincluding writing pupil reports (29%
OL,16,Fvs 11%), communicating with parents
OL,17,F(19% vs 11%) and marking (12% vs 7%).
