OL,6,FThe survey also found gaps within the
OL,7,Fstate sector as teachers in schools
OL,8,Fwith the most affluent intakes were
OL,9,Fmore likely to report having had
OL,10,Fformal AI training than those with the
OL,11,Fleast affluent (26% vs 18%).
OL,13,FThe charity is calling on the
OL,14,FGovernment to closely monitor any
OL,15,Finequalities in access and use of AI
OL,16,Fbetween schools.
