OL,4,Cschools in AI 'digital divide' ` report
OL,6,FThe Sutton Trust report said: "Private
OL,7,Fschools or those in wealthier areas
OL,8,Fare likely to have greater access to
OL,9,Fresources, and therefore be able to
OL,10,Fafford to invest both time and money
OL,11,Fin more sophisticated AI solutions."
OL,13,FIt added: "Action is urgently needed
OL,14,Fby Government to ensure that AI acts
OL,15,Fas a gap-closer, rather than a further
OL,16,Ffactor that exacerbates the already
OL,17,Fgrowing attainment gap between poorer
OL,18,Fstudents and their better-off peers."
