OL,3,CState schools falling behind private
OL,4,Cschools in AI 'digital divide' ` report
OL,6,FNick Harrison, chief executive of the
OL,7,FSutton Trust, said: "It's startling
OL,8,Fhow rapidly an AI digital divide is
OL,9,Fopening up in schools.
OL,11,F"This is a crucial time in integrating
OL,12,FAI tools into teaching, yet private
OL,13,Fschools, and some of the most affluent
OL,14,Fstate schools, are already forging
OL,15,Fahead in a sort of digital wild west.
OL,17,F"If this isn't quickly tackled head
OL,18,Fon, schools serving the most
OL,19,Fdisadvantaged pupils risk falling
OL,20,Ffurther behind.
OL,26,@oD@UOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
