OL,3,CState schools falling behind private
OL,4,Cschools in AI 'digital divide' ` report
OL,6,F"These tools can provide a range of
OL,7,Fbenefits to overworked teachers, but
OL,8,Ftheir use is spread unevenly, with
OL,9,Finequalities in training and
OL,10,Fappropriate guidance and monitoring.
OL,12,F"If action isn't taken to close these
OL,13,Fwidening gaps, access to AI risks
OL,14,Fbecoming the next major barrier to
OL,15,Fopportunity for disadvantaged young
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,18,F"The type of school you go to
OL,19,Fshouldn't determine your chances of
OL,20,Fbenefiting from AI in education."
