OL,6,F"We recognise that the Government is
OL,7,Ftaking some steps to support the
OL,8,Fsector with the development of AI but
OL,9,Fschools are battling against the twin
OL,10,Fproblems of funding and staffing
OL,11,Fcrises which leaves many overwhelmed.
OL,13,F"We need to see a much more sustained
OL,14,Fand strategic investment in schools
OL,15,Fand colleges which gives them time to
OL,16,Fbreathe and allows them to harness the
OL,17,Fpotential benefits of this technology."
