OL,6,FA Department for Education (DfE)
OL,7,Fspokeswoman said: "We are putting
OL,8,Fcutting-edge AI tools into the hands
OL,9,Fof teachers to ensure every young
OL,10,Fperson, regardless of what school they
OL,11,Fattend, benefits from the latest
OL,12,Ftechnology.
OL,14,F"We are supporting teachers by
OL,15,Fpublishing AI guidance and support
OL,16,Fmaterials to help schools and colleges
OL,17,Fuse AI safely and effectively, driving
OL,18,Fhigh standards breaking down barriers
OL,19,Fto opportunity so every child can
OL,20,Fachieve and thrive."
